1351	/// Create-from-empty orchestrator for the default dual shape.
1352	///
1353	/// Composes (in order):
1354	/// - Code side: `prepare_local_repo` → `write_code_config` →
1355	///   `commit_initial` (`OchidStrategy::Placeholder`).
1356	/// - Session side: `prepare_local_repo` → `write_session_config`
1357	///   → `commit_initial` (`OchidStrategy::Placeholder`).
